Kaz’s crew is the only thing that might stand between the world and destruction—if they don’t kill each other first.', CAST(N'2017-10-11T00:00:00.0000000' AS DateTime2), NULL, NULL, NULL, N'c0716c61-5ebd-4030-9baa-46fbeeaa448f.pdf', 0, CAST(N'2022-05-09T10:59:31.9836876' AS DateTime2), N'40e0cba1-5cc5-4035-b259-8d7268211ec6', CAST(N'2022-05-09T10:59:31.9836879' AS DateTime2), N'40e0cba1-5cc5-4035-b259-8d7268211ec6', 235, 7, 0)
